<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Task 3: Responsive Design</title>
    
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">

    <style>
        /* Smooth scrolling for the whole page */
        html {
            scroll-behavior: smooth;
        }

        /* Custom animation for the Hero Text */
        @keyframes fadeInDown {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(-20px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }
        
        .animated-header {
            animation: fadeInDown 1s ease-out forwards;
        }

        /* Advanced CSS Transition for Cards */
        .feature-card {
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
            border: none;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }

        /* When you hover over the card, it lifts up and the shadow grows */
        .feature-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
            box-shadow: 0 12px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-light">

    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-dark bg-dark sticky-top">
        <div class="container">
            <a class="navbar-brand" href="#">MyApp</a>
            <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#navbarNav">
                <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
            </button>
            <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarNav">
                <ul class="navbar-nav ms-auto">
                    <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="/">Task 1</a></li>
                    <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="/task2">Task 2</a></li>
                    <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link active" href="/task3">Task 3</a></li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <header class="bg-primary text-white text-center py-5 mb-5">
        <div class="container py-5">
            <h1 class="display-4 fw-bold animated-header">Welcome to Level 2</h1>
            <p class="lead">Exploring Advanced CSS, Bootstrap Grids, and Smooth Animations.</p>
            <a href="#features" class="btn btn-light btn-lg mt-3">Explore Features</a>
        </div>
    </header>

    <div class="container mb-5" id="features">
        <h2 class="text-center mb-4">Why Responsive Design Matters</h2>
        
        <div class="row g-4">
            
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="card h-100 feature-card p-3">
                    <div class="card-body text-center">
                        <h3 class="card-title text-primary">📱 Mobile First</h3>
                        <p class="card-text">This layout automatically stacks vertically on mobile phones, ensuring users never have to pinch or zoom to read the text.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="card h-100 feature-card p-3">
                    <div class="card-body text-center">
                        <h3 class="card-title text-success">🎨 Clean UI</h3>
                        <p class="card-text">By utilizing Bootstrap, we get access to beautifully proportioned typography, spacing, and colors right out of the box.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="card h-100 feature-card p-3">
                    <div class="card-body text-center">
                        <h3 class="card-title text-danger">✨ Animations</h3>
                        <p class="card-text">Hover over these cards! The custom CSS transitions make the elements feel interactive and alive.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>

    <footer class="bg-dark text-white text-center py-3 mt-auto">
        <div class="container">
            <p class="mb-0">&copy; 2026 My Full Stack Internship. Task 3 Complete.</p>
        </div>
    </footer>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>